cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.DB

This paper is about word embeddings for medical concepts, which is a natural language processing task. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of large amounts of data and the combination of different modalities, which suggests that cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are also likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with data management and organization, which could fall under cs.DB (Databases) and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
